==Cheng Feng 

~~~
{}{img_left}{pictures/Cheng_Feng-modified.png}{alt text}{220}{220}

I am currently Eric and Wendy Schmidt AI for Science Postdoctoral Fellow, College of Engineering, Cornell University, working with Prof. Fengqi You. \n 

I received the B.S. degree in Electrical Engineering from Huazhong University of Science and Technology in June 2019, and the Ph.D. degree in Electrical Engineering from Tsinghua University in June 2024. During February 2023 to August 2023, I was a visiting scholar in the Automatic Control Laboratory, ETH Zurich. Here is my [https://github.com/VictorCFeng/Page/blob/master/postdoc.pdf CV]\n

The publications of mine can be easily found on Google scholar and ResearchGate. Welcome discussions about my research! \n

