== Research
~~~
{}{img_left}{pictures/Research.png}{Cyber-Physical Energy Systems Overview}{590}{320}


*Grid Flexibility & Resilience*:  
Investigates the synergy between communication and power networks to enhance grid flexibility and resilience through advanced optimization and control strategies.
{{<img src="pictures/Direction1.png" width="300" />}} 


*Power Electronics & New Loads*
Explores the stability challenges and market mechanisms associated with the integration of inverter-based resources and high-demand loads, such as data centers. 
{{<img src="pictures/Direction2.png" width="300" />}} 


*Energy Digitization*
Drives the digital transformation of energy systems by leveraging Generative AI and Edge AI for smart industrial applications.
{{<img src="pictures/Direction3.png" width="300" />}} 
